==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Persnickety
<hw>Per*snick"et*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Finicky or fussy; demanding excessive attention to petty details or
niceties; unduly particular; fastidious; -- of people.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> finical, finicky, fussy, meticulous, painstaking,
pernickety, pernicketty, punctilious.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Snobbish; behaving aloofly.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pernickety, pernicketty.</syn>
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Persolve</ent>⟦br⟧
